resources.string:
"Thank you for using Alarmy!
We take your personal information and privacy protection very seriously.
In order to better protect your personal rights and interests, please carefully read all terms of <a href=\"https://alar.my/terms_and_conditions_cn.html\">Terms & Conditions</a> and <a href=\"https://alar.my/privacy_policy_cn.html\">Privacy Policy</a>, especially:
1. Our rules and regulations on the collection/storage/use/external provision/protection of your personal information, as well as your user rights and other terms;
2. Agreed on our limited liability and disclaimer clauses;
If you agree to the above terms, please click Accept to enter the app. Otherwise, click Deny."
